</p></sec></sec><sec id="S4"><title>Complications and postoperative knee function</title><p>No any complication (deep vein thrombosis, infection and wound complication) was found in our present study. No significant difference in postoperative knee function scores at 3-month and 6-month periods between groups (<xref ref-type="table" rid="T4">Table 4</xref>).</p><p>
